data.description: **OFFER DEADLINE - Saturday 2/10/24 at 8 pm   -   Seller reserves the right to choose an offer prior to deadline** Priced to sell!!!   Welcome home to your 3 bedroom, 2 & 1/2 bathroom townhome located conveniently to shopping and dining!  Not your typical cookie cutter town home, has some unique features to set you aside from other homes!  Stone flooring upon entering welcomes you to the family room with light from the afternoon sunshine!   Carpet replaced recently throughout the home.   Kitchen comes equipped with tile flooring and an  area for eating!   The dining room is placed adjacent to the kitchen for larger family gatherings.  Upstairs, you will be pleased with the newer flooring throughout.  Both upstairs bathrooms have been renovated for modernization.  Main bedroom is generously sized to accomodate a king size bed and furniture.  The two other bedrooms are facing the back with the afternoon sunlight!  The outdoor patio has been added for those summer evenings to enjoy a patio dinner or to enjoy the sunlight!!  For QUALIFIED buyers, take advantage of GMM's Welcome home/Journey $10,000 grant to help MAKE this HAPPEN!
